{"tid":1466353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼等於分化","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T13:52:47.000Z","uid":302780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"572702a0af98e5fdd065ed13d29caadd409c314d","tid":1466353,"uid":302780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"就算比你confirm到佢係鬼你可以做啲乜?<br />\n呢度係機場係乜人都有，有公安有警察有大陸人，係正常㗎 wo，其實一路都有㗎啦，運動咪照樣繼續。<br />\n<br />\n做自己本身要做既野，唔好理啲鬼啦"},{"pid":"229ca2debc750a7ea273e99a7574c7fdaec39ab6","tid":1466353,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077d99debde8ae6bc7449f5c97f39a3e0fb0fb50","tid":1466353,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"條友仲開記招！ 非法禁固呀家陣, 搵人提佢收皮啦 危險呀"},{"pid":"ef3c2efb03f4446aed964ef6b7fcf585f25e3a12","tid":1466353,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼 係捉唔晒既</span>"},{"pid":"5250d3b72d42a1e27487419f49b98e73f592c6cf","tid":1466353,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"雨傘運動輸咗係咁捉鬼 失焦<br />\n辛辛苦苦過去咗嘅兩個月<br />\n傷嘅傷 被捕嘅被捕 失去嘅失去<br />\n唔好再講乜野鬼唔鬼啦<br />\n811 有鬼做示威者開始就知一直都有鬼<br />\n我地做好自己要做嘅野咪得囉<br />\n集中返五大訴求<br />\n818再次上街"},{"pid":"3578deeae9b6e294463fcbb827fcda0deecc5643","tid":1466353,"uid":144272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"無錯，鬼無可能捉得哂。<br />\n<br />\n事情既然發生了，不要再往後望，要向前看。<br />\n<br />\n相比政府日日出來卜咪講大話，今日的算什麼？做好檢討，重新focus翻5大訴求！"},{"pid":"274435d13bebdec3f613bbdad357bbacbf82527d","tid":1466353,"uid":284480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}